RunDynamicEnrichment

Source: R/SCP-analysis.R
RunDynamicEnrichment.Rd

RunDynamicEnrichment

Usage

RunDynamicEnrichment(
  srt,
  lineages,
  score_method = "AUCell",
  ncore = 1,
  slot = "data",
  assay = "RNA",
  min_expcells = 20,
  r.sq = 0.2,
  dev.expl = 0.2,
  padjust = 0.05,
  geneID = NULL,
  IDtype = "symbol",
  species = "Homo_sapiens",
  enrichment = "GO_BP",
  db_update = FALSE,
  db_version = "latest",
  Ensembl_version = 103,
  mirror = NULL,
  TERM2GENE = NULL,
  TERM2NAME = NULL,
  minGSSize = 10,
  maxGSSize = 500,
  BPPARAM = BiocParallel::bpparam(),
  progressbar = TRUE,
  seed = 11
)

Arguments

seed
